OL,6,F2001 Following the takeover of HTV by
OL,7,FCarlton in October 2000, HTV's on air
OL,8,Fbranding remained untouched for a
OL,9,Fnumber of months. Until now.JAdapted
OL,10,Fversions of the spinning hearts idents
OL,11,Fwere aired for the first time today.
OL,12,FThe new ident sequences featured the
OL,13,Fsoundtrack from the Carlton idents
OL,14,Fused in the Midlands and London.JAnd
OL,15,Fwhilst they opened with the same
OL,16,Fvisuals as the London/Midlands idents,
OL,17,Fthe initial animation transitioned to
OL,18,Fthe spinning hearts/HTV logo animation
OL,19,Ffrom the previous set of HTV idents.
